metadata.description: LSD Mind Miners are explorers of the inner universe, using the powerful tool of lysergic acid diethylamide (LSD) to delve deep into the depths of their own minds. These brave adventurers are on a quest to discover the hidden treasures of consciousness, and to unlock the secrets of the human experience. Join them on their journey, and experience the mind-expanding power of LSD.
metadata.name: LSD MIND MINERS #1
